  {
    num:   '01',
    title: 'Site Visit',
    icon: `<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.54 22.35a1 1 0 01-1.08 0l-5.66-5.66a9 9 0 1112.4 0l-5.66 5.66zM11 12a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />`,
    body:  'Our engineer visits your property to inspect structural readiness, measure solar exposure, and assess your current energy consumption.',
  },
  {
    num:   '02',
    title: 'Design',
    image: '/how_design.png',
    icon: `<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2 10a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 110 2H3a1 1 0 01-1-1zM9 8a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 110 2h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1zM16 12a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 110 2h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1z" /><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 2a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h4v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h4a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm14 12H4V4h14v10z" clip-rule="evenodd" />`,
    body:  'We prepare a detailed module layout, single-line diagrams, expected generation metrics, and a precise financial payback model.',
  },
  {
    num:   '03',
    title: 'Approval',
    image: '/how_approve.png',
    icon: `<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12zm13.707-3.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L11 10.586 9.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />`,
    body:  'We manage DISCOM grid connectivity approvals, net-metering agreements, and register you on the PM Surya Ghar national portal.',
  },
  {
    num:   '04',
    title: 'Installation',
    image: '/how_installation.png',
    icon: `<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M19.5 21a3 3 0 003-3v-4.5a3 3 0 00-3-3h-1.5V9a3 3 0 00-3-3H9a3 3 0 00-3 3v1.5H4.5A3 3 0 001.5 13.5V18a3 3 0 003 3h15zM6 9a1.5 1.5 0 011.5-1.5h9A1.5 1.5 0 0118 9v1.5H6V9zm12 6H6v3h12v-3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />`,
    body:  'Our certified engineering team deploys the system with zero disruption. We commission the plant and deliver all compliance papers.',
  },
  {
    num:   '05',
    title: 'Savings',
    image: '/how_saving.png',
    icon: `<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1.75 5.5a2.75 2.75 0 00-2.75 2.75V11h3.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5H11v.75a2.75 2.75 0 002.75 2.75h.5c.96 0 1.75-.78 1.75-1.75a.75.75 0 011.5 0c0 1.56-1.12 2.87-2.6 3.16L17.2 20.2a.75.75 0 11-1.2.9l-3.1-4.13a.75.75 0 01-.15-.47V15H9.5a.75.75 0 010-1.5h3.25a1.25 1.25 0 01-1.25-1.25V11H9.5a.75.75 0 010-1.5h2.16c.38-1.56 1.78-2.75 3.47-2.75a.75.75 0 010 1.5h-.88z" clip-rule="evenodd" />`,
    body:  'Activate real-time app tracking. Start saving from Month 1 while we handle scheduled O&M audits to keep output at peak levels.',
  },
